      <title>由于政府拒绝债券持有人的提议，斯里兰卡债务重组陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/sri-lanka-fails-agree-restructuring-terms-with-bondholders-2024-04-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡周二拒绝了国际债券持有人重组超过120亿美元债务的提议，这使得国际货币基金组织(IMF)的关键支持面临风险，并推迟了解决长达两年的债务危机的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/sri-lanka-fails-agree-restructuring-terms-with-bondholders-2024-04-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 12:10:45 GMT</pubDate>
